## Provider

- `repository_provider.dart` — single entry for auth/court/profile repos.
- API mode (`USE_LEGACY_SUPABASE=false`): `ApiAuthRepository`, `CourtRepository`, `ProfileRepository`.
- Legacy: `SupabaseAuthRepository` + `court_services.dart`.

## API mode endpoints

| Repo | Method | HTTP |
|------|--------|------|
| `ApiAuthRepository` | login/register | `POST /auth/login`, `/auth/register` |
| `ApiAuthRepository` | logout | `POST /auth/logout` |
| `ProfileRepository` | profile CRUD | `GET/PUT /profiles/me` |
| `CourtRepository` | list/create | `GET/POST /courts` |

## Patterns

- HTTP base: `API_BASE_URL` dart-define (see `baller_app/README.md`).
- Tokens: `flutter_secure_storage` via `baller_app/lib/core/api/token_storage.dart` — never `SharedPreferences`.
- New feature: add `backend/app/routers/*` endpoint + repository method together.

## Do not

- Bypass `AuthGate` in `main.dart`.
- Add `Supabase.instance.client` table access for new API-mode features.
